{"word":"Lot","slug":"lot","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Lot</b> <a href=\"#/H3876\">H3876</a><br/><a href=\"#/G3091\">G3091</a> <br/> 1. Feast of<br/> <a href='S:Purim'>Purim</a><br/> 2. The son of Haran:<br/> - Accompanies Terah from Ur of the Chaldees to Haran<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=31'>Gen 11:31</a> <br/> - Migrates with Abraham to the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=4'>Gen 12:4</a> <br/> - Accompanies Abraham to Egypt; returns with him to Beth-El<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=3'>Gen 13:3</a> <br/> - Rich in flocks, and herds, and servants; separates from Abraham, and locates in Sodom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=14'>Gen 13:14</a> <br/> - Taken captive by Chedorlaomer; rescued by Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=16'>Gen 14:16</a> <br/> - Providentially saved from destruction in Sodom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19'>Gen 19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=17&verse=29'>Luk 17:29</a> <br/> - Disobediently protests against going to the mountains, and chooses Zoar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=22'>Gen 19:22</a> <br/> - His wife disobediently longs after Sodom, and becomes a pillar of salt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=26'>Gen 19:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=17&verse=32'>Luk 17:32</a> <br/> - Commits incest with his daughters<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=38'>Gen 19:38</a> <br/> - Descendants of<br/> <a href='S:Ammonites'>Ammonites</a>; <a href='S:Moabites'>Moabites</a> <br/>Lot the, General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=16&verse=33'>Pro 16:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=18&verse=18'>Pro 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=34&verse=17'>Isa 34:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=3'>Joe 3:3</a><br/> The scapegoat chosen by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=10'>Lev 16:10</a><br/> The land of Canaan divided among the tribes by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=55'>Num 26:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15'>Jos 15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=10'>Jos 18:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=51'>Jos 19:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21'>Jos 21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=61'>1Ch 6:61</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=65'>1Ch 6:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=1'>Eze 45:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=22'>Eze 47:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=48&verse=29'>Eze 48:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=2&verse=5'>Mic 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=19'>Act 13:19</a><br/> Saul chosen king by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=10&verse=21'>1Sa 10:21</a><br/> Priests and Levites designated by, for sanctuary service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=31'>1Ch 24:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=13'>1Ch 26:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=34'>Neh 10:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=9'>Luk 1:9</a><br/> Used after the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=1'>Neh 11:1</a><br/> An apostle chosen by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=26'>Act 1:26</a><br/> Instances of guilt ascertained by:<br/> - Achan's<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=18'>Jos 7:18</a> <br/> - Jonathan's<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=42'>1Sa 14:42</a> <br/> - Jonah's<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=7'>Jon 1:7</a> <br/> Used to fix the time for the execution of condemned persons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=3&verse=7'>Est 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=9&verse=24'>Est 9:24</a><br/> The garments of Jesus divided by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=22&verse=18'>Psa 22:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=35'>Mat 27:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=24'>Mar 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=24'>Joh 19:24</a>"}]}